Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see the trouble we're having with the body right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all because of the body, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my mouth and your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if we didn't all have bodies here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd just all be together in one big spiritual space,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.39,0:00:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you would all know what I know, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we'd have one mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd just all know what everybody else knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't even have to verbalize
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and go through all this whole talking-ness business,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,which I do for the sake of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But it takes an espresso to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.54,0:01:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the healings that people have,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the result is not the time for them to leave this earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're destined to leave at a certain time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,then you can either leave in good condition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.62,0:01:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or not such good condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you about the old people in the nursing home,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, saying, help, help, help, help, help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, and they got a stroke on this side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and a stroke on this side,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're paralyzed with rheumatism all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Their kidneys are gone, their heart's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't hear or see or smell anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're still going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And then when the time comes, you can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The door to the airplane opens up at 36,000 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,One person is withdrawn from that airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, that was in the papers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,about 10, 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was the stewardess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,D.C., whatever it is, at 36,000 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The door suddenly blew open,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and exactly one person was extracted
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the 350 passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So when karmically it's your time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you ain't going to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it isn't time, you can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're conditioned at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So the time of leaving is karmically set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're conditioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other factors,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.62,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they're up to personal choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,what will be helpful to keep in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,if one leaves a higher level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and moves to a lower level of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You change your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You change your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like somebody only went to fifth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away, your expectation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you shift your intellectual presentation to them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so they can comprehend it out of compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of compassion for somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,who's struggling,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with the barest minimum of existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I modify how I present a concept to them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so that it is mutually, meets mutual needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,not just my needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we like to tell everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,how democracy is so wonderful and this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's meaningful to somebody in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's meaningful to somebody in the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To somebody who doesn't know where dinner is going
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to come from tonight, it's so much palaver, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been in places, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about South America on the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not very left-brained right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you the name of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikenema Beach, or what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What country is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Brazil, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,On the side of the mountains there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the favelas where the peasants live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how they live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole family of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where they live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a piece of tin here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's some string.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some paper there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here, it looks like some used toilet paper, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind that is a piece of cardboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind that is a couple of bricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind that is some stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten people live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I give you a lecture on democracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You stated that you had been to hell, and you felt this terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but you never saw an entity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So what created terror?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the Buddha and Jesus Christ recommended,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jesus and the Buddha both said,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,avoid that which makes you go weak with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that because they said that the spirit, after it leaves the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:05:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,will pay the karmic consequences for your decisions and choices in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, it wasn't like they were trying to create a fear of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,although religions have done so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In this particular lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the extreme, there's been great spiritual extremes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, at age three, there was a confrontation that only occurs at level 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out of many lifetimes as a Hinayana Buddhist,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in which I followed the pathway of negation with great dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And to me, at that time, the ultimate reality was the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, each lifetime, I would go out into the void, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If the void was real,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there would have been nobody to report such an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, because it's not real, you can't stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So the void is very, very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you constantly negate everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you eventually go into a state of nothingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is so overwhelmingly impressive, you're sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the ultimate goal of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what a terror is then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing there to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no terror in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I turned away from it in this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,because already at age 12,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.48,0:06:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd had the experience of the infinite oneness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and the most memorable quality was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're melted by the,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,by the divine love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think any words in that state,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but the love melts any,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so the mind is silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it's melted out by divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the state was not recoverable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't talk about personal experience today,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because it did not seem relevant to the lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but later on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,well later on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the sequence of events then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so it makes some kind of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, walking through the,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very religious spiritually,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,high Episcopal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a boy acolyte,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,a boy soprano with a cathedral,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and extremely religious,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and scrupulous in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One day walking through the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden the world was silent and still,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,like an infinite presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden out of nowhere came
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,a non-verbal awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw the totality,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to describe this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:08:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the totality of the suffering of all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a massive,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,non-verbal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,massive awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and I grasped the totality of the suffering of all of man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In that instant I became a profound atheist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,any God that can allow that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,or create that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,in the mind of the child,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,see,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,especially Christianity in the 1930s,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the idea was that God creates everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,see,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore all tortures,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and sin is the product of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sophisticated,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize that all the suffering of man
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is the product of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,not of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So what I was looking at was the totality
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of the production of the ego over time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the mass of suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is beyond description.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I held God responsible for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so I instantly became an atheist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't realize I was looking at the product of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and not the product of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a very intense atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I then went to a Jesuit university
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,where I got straight A in theology.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The better to argue the stupidity of theology
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and the idiocy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of Aristotle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and St. Thomas Aquinas,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,of primary cause
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and all that idiotic childish intellectualization,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,which I blew out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was like an intense preoccupation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with a knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was an essential truth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that was reachable,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was unable to reach it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and thereby intense effort
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally went into a sense of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,about the inability to contact
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the core of truth of existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess driven by the phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that I experienced at age three,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd forgotten about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,in searching for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,some kind of an ultimate answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I went into a profound state of actual hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I investigated all the levels of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,including the depths of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and driven into hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,as a Dante,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,how Dante knew the nature of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked whether he'd been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was absolutely accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As I went into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the upper layers of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,have to do with chopping people up and torture
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and sort of Saddam Hussein's son's kind of deviltry,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which are just jacks for openers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,chopping people up and torching them to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that's hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the warning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're getting close to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it really gets severe,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it gets agonizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.27,0:11:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the agony reaches beyond what you can bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it suddenly gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.27,0:11:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,almost like you see a sign that says,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,abandon all hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,ye who enter here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Dante wrote those exact words,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I saw those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you enter a level of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's imagination can imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of horrific despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the highest levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,are forever and beyond time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the lowest depths of hell are timeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you are in the absolute hopeless despair
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,with no hope ever of getting out of this state,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you begin to realize what forever means.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the horror of where you're at hits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At that level of hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond all description,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,out of this consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the prayer arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a God,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget I was a profound atheist at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a God,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask him to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there was oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometime later,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether it was hours or a day or what,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it was a complete and total transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in which a personal self had dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was only awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,being the totality and allness of the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,as all existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The stunning beauty of it left one speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind no longer existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The tail end of the mind disappeared into the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The tail end of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,was struck dumb with awe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The revelation of the splendor of the existence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as all existence and all of its stunning beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,shone forth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and blew out whatever remained of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and fried it out forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's never had the audacity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to think a thought since.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So what remains to speak then
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is a presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,which is silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If I listen to the mind now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it says nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just an infinite silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But the intentionality of expression
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,coming out of your question,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,for instance,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the answering this is happening
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own spontaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I myself have nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some heavy stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Two quick questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,if you and Werner Erhard
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,are familiar with each other's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm familiar with Werner's work, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Werner Erhard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people here have done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How many have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all the older people here have done this, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The younger ones are too young to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was great fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody did it back in the 70s, I think it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's by a different name now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also wondering if you knew of the work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the wisdom teachings of Avatar Adidas Samraj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wondering if you knew of the wisdom teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of Avatar Adidas Samraj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a million gurus out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't calculate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said Ramana Maharshi at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was one of his...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Ramana Maharshi and Asagadatta Maharaj
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,both calibrated in the low 700s.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,700 is the level of sage, sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't usually change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The sage usually goes in at 700,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,usually never leaves where they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and stays there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See, consciousness tends to revolve of its own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you can go into bliss state
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's absolutely perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no necessity to go any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And consciousness may or may not stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, 50% of the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the person just leaves the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.97,0:15:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely rarely, extremely rarely,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,extremely, extremely rarely,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,only a few in every generation or century even,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,does consciousness then start moving
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,from like 700 to 800 to 900 to 1000.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And it does it of its own accord,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,unasked,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's no one there to ask it to move ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no incompleteness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason when you're sitting there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in a state of complete and total bliss
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the infinite holiness of the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to suspect that consciousness could move
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere than where it is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's complete and total from moment to moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing I forgot to explain about
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,how one experiences reality
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the Newtonian paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is always incomplete
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.52,0:16:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and moving to completeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you let go of that paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you stop projecting that onto phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that because all is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all represents creation, continuous creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what you now see is everything goes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from completeness to completeness to completeness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from perfection to perfection to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not go from imperfection to perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The half-unfolded rose is absolutely
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and perfectly and completely a half-unfolded rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect now, it's perfect now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it's perfect now, it's perfect now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it's perfect now, it's perfect now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it's perfect now, it's complete now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's perfect now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How it transforms, how you experience the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that everything is perfection
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,every instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that's going on in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is absolutely perfect right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,None of it should be or could be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,or is doing anything other than
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,what is at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We go from perfection to perfection,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,from completion to completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So we witness that way, creation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize that it's divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're witnessing divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and the unfolding of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for your contribution to humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:18:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the problem of abundance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's all these workshops on abundance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I do workshops on the problem of abundance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do with abundance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you drink three Pepsis at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you let go
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of the sense of incompleteness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and see everything is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that you are complete
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and total every instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.60,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have no further needs or desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody says,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to make up something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to make them happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a new bow tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now they're happy they have something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that they can get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,actually I have no need for a bow tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got drawers full of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got drawers full of bow ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the world's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,greatest collection of bow ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,once you see it correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,every moment you have all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that you need at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't have anything to eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have all that you need
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to starve to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hard one to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're meant to starve to death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,then what you need
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is the absence of food
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're provided with that need
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,by the absence of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you can happily starve to death
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,full of self-pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And hate God
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and now feel vindicated in hating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,With what you just said in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't need any answers to anything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you'd sign this book,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll give you a dollar, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.11,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your desires are already fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a divine dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mark this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never spend this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote special on that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a holy dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A holy dollar, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't have a question either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and ask you to sign my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be happy to sign it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's a gift to me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to allow me to sign your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I might use this dollar to save my life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you to sign my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Middle East calibrates now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,below the 200 level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any theories or ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,around how long it's going to take
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or what could be the catalyst
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to get them above 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't explain that fully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We really didn't get in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the shortage of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,how to transcend the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the ego is a substitute for God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we explained in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Egocentricity is,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it seeks to displace God as the authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, The Course in Miracles explains that very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the reason I like the Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it really explains the authority problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what was your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the ego then feeds off of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it is devoid of divine energizing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it's self-energizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And the ego survives,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,this is something important
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have said this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,by the juice it gets out of its positionalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets so much juice out of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should it give up hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.16,0:22:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch the two sides on the newsreel every night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,shooting at each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,throwing bricks at each other over the barricades.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Throwing rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,shooting at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in a state of high joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no higher joy than throwing rocks at the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can then provoke the police
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to finally let go of the dogs or shoot somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you can get on television with the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This justifies shooting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.28,0:22:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the payoff on this is tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And the leaders of those countries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,maintain their political position
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.99,0:22:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,based on playing this game endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that they've been at it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,since I've been on the planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.33,0:22:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been at it since I've been on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Same boundaries, same people,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.33,0:22:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,same justification, same ideology,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,same motivation, same payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.33,0:23:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's going to go on to perpetuity?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It could go on another thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the ego will juice everything out of injustice,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,remorse, revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The spleen is a very strong chakra in those regions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you might say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,those are regions that live in the chakra of the spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatred, envy, jealousy, untruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How long can they live there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do nothing but signing books
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,after we get a few more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what we should do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, but the questions can go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll just have people sign books real fast
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so we can sign a lot of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can still talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.03,0:23:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll be happy to hug you all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and answer as many questions as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My ambition is to hug everybody who's here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll make it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was going to ask for a handshake,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'll take the hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so at the instant we're born,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.50,0:24:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we come in with a certain level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.50,0:24:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and we come in with a predetermined time of our death,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.50,0:24:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so we might as well not think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.50,0:24:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then for want of another word,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.50,0:24:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we come in with this soul that has karmic potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.50,0:24:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said the soul or this karmic potential
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is influenced by conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.50,0:24:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of the field of infamy, of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.50,0:24:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of whatever term you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.50,0:24:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my question to you is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.50,0:24:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,in this karmic soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.21,0:25:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,can I have any influence on that field
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.21,0:25:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and is my influence based on will and choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.21,0:25:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you phrased it exactly correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.26,0:25:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but you won't influence the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.26,0:25:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But in other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.29,0:25:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I picture this life as purgatorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.29,0:25:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we have a huge range of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.29,0:25:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huge range of choice at every instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.80,0:25:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we have our karmic potential
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.80,0:25:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have our karmic obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.03,0:25:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already born with a certain IQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.03,0:25:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're born with a certain kind of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.03,0:25:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an endomorph, mesomorph, or ectomorph.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.03,0:25:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're born with a certain IQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.03,0:25:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are born genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.03,0:25:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are born not so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.44,0:25:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people are born strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.44,0:25:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are born weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.50,0:25:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are born rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.50,0:25:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are born poor, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.85,0:25:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, starting out,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.85,0:25:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you find yourself again in a physical body
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.61,0:25:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in a human lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.61,0:26:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The choices that are karmically destined to come up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.61,0:26:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,will come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.61,0:26:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time you have a choice to answer differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.61,0:26:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This time you have a choice to answer differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.09,0:26:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All the choices, all my choices,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.09,0:26:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,are karmic choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.09,0:26:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't exist without choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.09,0:26:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so everything that I choose
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.09,0:26:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything I think is a karmic choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.09,0:26:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.64,0:26:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.64,0:26:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,there's various levels to this question.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.64,0:26:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There are certain patterns which are inherent
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.64,0:26:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,within the energy field of the spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.21,0:26:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,as it reincarnates.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.21,0:26:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of these karmic patterns
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.92,0:26:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,are going to be of greater importance
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.92,0:26:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or greater pressure than others.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.92,0:26:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are going to be trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.13,0:26:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Some are going to be surely optional.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.13,0:26:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you see, in a complex pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.13,0:26:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a small choice made here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.57,0:27:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,will put you in a different realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.57,0:27:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where other karmic propensities are going to come up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.57,0:27:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,where if you don't make that choice, it won't come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.57,0:27:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see an endless series
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.74,0:27:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,like a mosaic.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.76,0:27:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say yes to that, that puts me over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.76,0:27:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here I have these options.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.76,0:27:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say no to that, it puts me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.76,0:27:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here I don't have those options.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.76,0:27:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So from moment to moment
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.76,0:27:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am constantly determining my own karmic destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.76,0:27:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.76,0:27:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say yes to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.76,0:27:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I now have the option to say yes to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.76,0:27:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say no to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.76,0:27:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.76,0:27:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say no, I won't go to Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.76,0:27:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the option of walking the maze
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.76,0:27:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in Chartres Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.76,0:27:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm there, is it a maze?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.76,0:27:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.76,0:27:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an amazing place, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.76,0:27:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get there and I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.76,0:27:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll walk it while I'm there,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.76,0:27:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I get there, there's chairs all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.76,0:27:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, the church authorities don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.76,0:27:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,trails of people going out down the street
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.76,0:27:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,walking the maze, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.76,0:28:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the complex or whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.76,0:28:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So every choice then alters your options
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.76,0:28:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,from moment to moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.76,0:28:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the endlessness and the complexity
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.76,0:28:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,of the energy field of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.76,0:28:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But here's then the last point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.96,0:28:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That being the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.96,0:28:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.96,0:28:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,constantly weaving your way through
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.96,0:28:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,all the choices
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.96,0:28:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the concept of surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.96,0:28:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because one choice you have is to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.43,0:28:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is a choice that's present all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.49,0:28:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I'm experiencing pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.49,0:28:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can surrender the experience to God
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.49,0:28:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,or I can resist it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.49,0:28:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I resist it, that intensifies the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.49,0:28:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to disappear a thing is to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.49,0:28:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,let go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.96,0:28:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All experiencing comes out of resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.44,0:28:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the persistence of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.44,0:28:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that you experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.44,0:28:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember on that chart up there we put
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.44,0:29:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the witnesser, the experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.53,0:29:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing experiencing what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.53,0:29:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Within this entity whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.78,0:29:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.78,0:29:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What would it experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.26,0:29:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's conscious and aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.26,0:29:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not experiencing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.85,0:29:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bugger.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.00,0:29:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can see is getting your way through
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.74,0:29:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole endless complexity of choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.74,0:29:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And every choice determines your options.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.23,0:29:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, if I say yes to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.23,0:29:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that opens these options.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.23,0:29:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a mouse cannot decide
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.23,0:29:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to become a gopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.39,0:29:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's karmically already bound to certain choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.39,0:29:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you as a human being
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.39,0:29:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,inherit a body and a brain
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.39,0:29:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and your own karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.39,0:29:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So your choices are not unlimited.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.42,0:30:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot decide to become
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.92,0:30:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a champion wrestler right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.92,0:30:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.59,0:30:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.59,0:30:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess then, I guess then,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.59,0:30:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,this is pretty heavy,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.58,0:30:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but ideally, faith is realizing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.11,0:30:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you were to live only in the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.11,0:30:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,every single moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.11,0:30:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and every single moment you were to surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.11,0:30:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that's as close as you're going to come
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.63,0:30:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to enlightenment in this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.63,0:30:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to surrender
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.96,0:30:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and no one has surrendered too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.96,0:30:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.96,0:30:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the fact that you need to become enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.96,0:30:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is already a great illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.21,0:30:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you have to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.21,0:30:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I get very nervous in front of crowds
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.21,0:30:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm like, okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.21,0:30:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a newborn baby to all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.21,0:30:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you become more nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.21,0:31:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not nervous enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.21,0:31:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.21,0:31:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were really nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.30,0:31:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't be complaining about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.30,0:31:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.30,0:31:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.30,0:31:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.47,0:31:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the greatest lie of our time
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.47,0:31:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,right now that we have to be careful of,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.47,0:31:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Southern Baptist convert to Catholic,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.47,0:31:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so the fear of hell is ingrained, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.55,0:31:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, is that there is no hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.55,0:31:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.55,0:31:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,God is all loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.55,0:31:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,God is all forgiving.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.55,0:31:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had to narrow my faith down
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.55,0:31:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to where it was something I could live with.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.55,0:31:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I finally came up with
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.55,0:31:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,was the face in front of my face
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.55,0:31:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and intent is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.55,0:31:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, actions, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.92,0:31:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what you always heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.92,0:31:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,actions can't get me anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.92,0:31:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.45,0:31:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, your description of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.45,0:32:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,scared me to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.45,0:32:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back to the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.45,0:32:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.90,0:32:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't like it's a realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.34,0:32:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like it's a level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.44,0:32:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you're still within
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.44,0:32:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the realm of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.75,0:32:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To abandon God, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.75,0:32:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is to throw yourself at the mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.75,0:32:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of word consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.92,0:32:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There are regions of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.36,0:32:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that you really don't want to experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.36,0:32:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.36,0:32:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.60,0:32:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, you described hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.60,0:32:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're really saying is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.60,0:32:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,hell most definitely exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.60,0:32:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.60,0:32:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's personalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.60,0:32:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell is personalized for each individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.60,0:32:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.60,0:32:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If they choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.60,0:32:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If they choose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.60,0:32:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.19,0:32:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But hell does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.25,0:32:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And experientially,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.27,0:32:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,both heaven and hell are experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.27,0:32:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're purely subjective.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.27,0:33:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.75,0:33:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only subjectivity that even,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.75,0:33:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,could even say they exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.92,0:33:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You say they exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.92,0:33:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.92,0:33:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.92,0:33:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.92,0:33:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.92,0:33:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, you know, said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.92,0:33:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.11,0:33:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone can just sit back and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.11,0:33:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Lean into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.68,0:33:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor tells me this
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.68,0:33:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,counts out about seven, seven-fifty, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.11,0:33:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.21,0:41:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what the whole lecture's about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.63,0:41:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be willing to surrender the juice
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.63,0:41:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that you get out of the ego's positionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.63,0:42:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be willing to surrender the juice of self-pity,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.63,0:42:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the juice of resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.63,0:42:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the juice of hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.63,0:42:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the juice of getting even.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.63,0:42:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All the negative payoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.73,0:42:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're willing to surrender the negative payoffs to the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.73,0:42:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you dissolve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.73,0:42:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds simple enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.01,0:42:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.01,0:42:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't get into that in the lecture today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.01,0:42:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, thanks for all the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.71,0:42:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.71,0:42:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you sign a book and get a picture, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.71,0:42:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.98,0:42:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Doc, how did you lose that thumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.98,0:42:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, karmically, there's a story behind it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.98,0:42:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but actually I did it with a circular saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.98,0:42:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It kicked back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.17,0:42:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.17,0:42:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You always say, well, it's off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.17,0:42:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I couldn't get my hand out of the way in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.17,0:43:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If it starts to kick back, you don't have enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.17,0:43:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves faster than the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.30,0:43:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.78,0:43:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get a chance to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.78,0:43:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you got more books in your works?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.78,0:43:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one major book, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.78,0:43:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working on it for a year or two already.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.78,0:43:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to keep writing, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.78,0:43:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this one's going to take another year anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.07,0:43:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be a major buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.07,0:43:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.11,0:43:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, September 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.32,0:43:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.01,0:43:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.90,0:43:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.28,0:43:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful the field brought me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.28,0:43:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.28,0:43:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Many, many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.36,0:43:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.36,0:43:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be short.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.36,0:43:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.36,0:43:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one's an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.36,0:43:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.36,0:43:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.36,0:43:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.36,0:43:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.98,0:44:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.32,0:44:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is subjectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.36,0:44:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't get into that too heavily today, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.05,0:44:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So are you going to have a cigarette later?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.73,0:44:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to, yeah, if you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.73,0:44:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.73,0:44:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to get distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.73,0:44:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.73,0:44:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a ritual smoke together.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.73,0:44:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.73,0:44:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.73,0:44:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tribal custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.73,0:44:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's holy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.73,0:44:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.76,0:44:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Native American custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.53,0:44:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, David.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.53,0:44:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.53,0:44:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been reading your book.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.53,0:44:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.53,0:44:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.53,0:44:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.53,0:44:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.53,0:44:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I have many questions, but there's too many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.53,0:44:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.53,0:44:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Has been a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.53,0:44:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.53,0:44:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.53,0:44:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.53,0:44:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.53,0:44:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.53,0:44:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.53,0:44:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.53,0:44:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.36,0:44:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a blessing to hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.36,0:44:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm glad you enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.36,0:44:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have questions, too, but I'll come back sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.36,0:44:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If they ask easy ones, we can answer them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.36,0:44:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.36,0:44:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If they ask easy ones, but they ask these hard ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.36,0:44:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They think of such complicated questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.36,0:44:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.36,0:44:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that I would have asked had already been answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.36,0:45:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going to calibrate the audience before and after?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.42,0:45:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.42,0:45:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.42,0:45:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.42,0:45:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this audience at the end of the lecture was over 440, 444, 445.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.42,0:45:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,10 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.42,0:45:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.42,0:45:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.42,0:45:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.42,0:45:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.42,0:45:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.42,0:45:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.42,0:45:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.32,0:45:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.32,0:45:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.32,0:45:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.32,0:45:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.32,0:45:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.32,0:45:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.32,0:45:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,444.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.32,0:45:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,445.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.32,0:45:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,445.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.32,0:45:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,10 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.32,0:45:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.86,0:45:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,435 to 445.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.86,0:45:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that an average calibration?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.86,0:45:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.86,0:45:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An audience, 10 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.86,0:45:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some that are higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.86,0:45:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's some that are really low.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.86,0:45:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some really got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.86,0:45:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.86,0:45:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.86,0:45:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Some got it this much lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.86,0:45:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, some people went down, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.86,0:45:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the smarter ones went up 20 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.86,0:45:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.86,0:45:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are really listening did go up more than 10 points, but the average is 10
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.86,0:45:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,points, which is pretty good for a whole bunch of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.86,0:45:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.86,0:45:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.86,0:45:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.86,0:45:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.86,0:45:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.86,0:45:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.86,0:45:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.86,0:45:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.86,0:45:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.86,0:45:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for a whole field.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.30,0:45:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.44,0:45:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he leaving right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.21,0:45:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.38,0:46:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ralph, did you come down by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.15,0:46:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he brought a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.75,0:46:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.59,0:46:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He brought a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.42,0:46:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.15,0:46:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking good, Ralph.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.32,0:46:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking better.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.42,0:46:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.23,0:46:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your head is shinier.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.38,0:46:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It shows you're getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.86,0:46:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was the reason you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.36,0:46:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I was a reflective mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.34,0:46:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you do look better.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.36,0:46:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You look better, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.46,0:46:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.01,0:46:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So what does one do when they're by themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.75,0:46:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for the questions and the testing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.44,0:46:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I would use this system.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.05,0:46:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you find somebody to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.86,0:46:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You find somebody to work with.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.96,0:46:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And certain people work really well
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.07,0:46:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and easy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.86,0:46:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And other people don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.96,0:46:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So find somebody you just sort of work easy with, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.36,0:46:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And it sort of just automatically happens
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.25,0:46:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,when you find the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.21,0:47:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.55,0:47:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get your flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.75,0:47:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.17,0:47:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.78,0:47:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.67,0:47:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.51,0:47:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we sent you flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.17,0:47:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We might have been out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.28,0:47:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We were.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.11,0:47:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We were.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.96,0:47:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.48,0:47:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.32,0:47:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.32,0:47:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.26,0:47:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you bet. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.55,0:47:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.50,0:47:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.17,0:47:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished this book last night
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.09,0:47:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,when my dad died.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.40,0:47:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.23,0:47:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And it helped me to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.00,0:47:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,how much more joyous I am
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.30,0:47:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,than I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.13,0:47:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.21,0:47:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.42,0:47:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.42,0:47:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.51,0:47:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.57,0:47:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.42,0:47:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.21,0:47:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.05,0:47:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you a very quick question?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.15,0:47:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.98,0:47:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you talked about
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.01,0:47:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a set point
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.26,0:47:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for the time of our death, basically.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.55,0:47:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's already a set time for our death.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.53,0:47:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.40,0:47:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your question is, is there also a set point
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.51,0:48:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for where we will be on the map of consciousness at that point?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.44,0:48:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.71,0:48:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So freedom of choice, power of intention, free will,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.36,0:48:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,all that plays a part in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.57,0:48:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you come in with a calibrated level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.00,0:48:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That puts you somewhere in the field, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.40,0:48:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.34,0:48:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've got your options.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.40,0:48:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when you leave the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.53,0:48:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to gravitate to that which you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.44,0:48:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So a person who has gravitated to hatred and hating God
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.84,0:48:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,will automatically find himself in the realm of hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.80,0:48:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,God doesn't condemn him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.63,0:48:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who chooses gentleness and love
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.80,0:48:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is automatically going to gravitate to people who are gentle and loving, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.98,0:48:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like some people...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.76,0:48:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.82,0:48:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.40,0:48:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people like, you know, the quiet, peaceful, rural.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.90,0:48:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So they automatically are going to move there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.09,0:48:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not going to hang out in New York City, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.01,0:48:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people like the excitement of New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.94,0:49:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the high of the solar plexus.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.61,0:49:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So they live in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.82,0:49:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.51,0:49:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.13,0:49:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've never alluded to this in any of your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.71,0:49:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but did Jesus ever come to you and guide you in the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.84,0:49:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What will?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.67,0:49:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Jesus ever come to you and guide you in the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.32,0:49:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.76,0:49:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she was afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.38,0:49:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She was afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.28,0:49:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She was afraid of the end of the line, and then she didn't have the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.01,0:49:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She was afraid of everybody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.28,0:49:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.50,0:49:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.86,0:49:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See, as a consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.76,0:49:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need some more drinks, water?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.51,0:49:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.59,0:49:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As a consciousness, a great consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.03,0:49:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of Jesus makes itself known all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.07,0:49:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and is always available.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.44,0:49:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.65,0:49:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus is present right here at this moment in between the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.65,0:49:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to ask you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.65,0:49:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't drink that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.90,0:50:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The body of Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.90,0:50:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot on the body of Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.90,0:50:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The body of Jesus is just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.90,0:50:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The body of physicality means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.90,0:50:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone, like, could go to bed or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.90,0:50:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look that up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.90,0:50:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality of Christ is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.90,0:50:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness that supports our consciousness as we speak
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.59,0:50:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is already present.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.59,0:50:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me, when I was a little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.28,0:50:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,he came in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.53,0:50:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.53,0:50:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to me when I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.53,0:50:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to my room.
